RT by @sidhant: Nepal’s Foreign Minister Shisir Khanal has signalled a fresh, forward-looking approach to relations with India, emphasising opportunities in trade, connectivity, technology and energy as the two neighbours seek to firm up ties under new leadership in Kathmandu

Speaking to WION's @sidhant during a visit that included meetings with top Indian officials, Khanal said Nepal’s new government, backed by a strong mandate, was determined not to be held back by history

